{"tid":763664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實連登仔點睇國民黨?","createTime":"2018-08-01T10:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T13:26:45.000Z","uid":70429,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"bf6ff298f2fc82a54d82e1b77e73712288f88161","tid":763664,"uid":70429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T10:10:01.000Z","msg":"個個都非黑即白覺得共產黨仆街 = 國民黨好.<br />\n<br />\n見到依個邏輯就覺得好吊詭,<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明明國民黨內部任人唯親,國家比四大姓財閥壟斷市場,選舉貪污舞弊,官僚主義,議會,法治,政治全部都一批人壟斷,真正既共和國家下出現一言堂.<br />\n<br />\n物價每年通脹以倍數計,最尾講緊一萬倍通脹,民國末年出現買一斤米要用五斤紙幣買,甚至法幣用來點煙炆屎既情況.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gtimg.com/finance/pics/hv1/153/31/666/43314708.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gtimg.com%2Ffinance%2Fpics%2Fhv1%2F153%2F31%2F666%2F43314708.jpg&h=b20497d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://timg01.bdimg.com/timg?pacompress&amp;imgtype=1&amp;sec=1439619614&amp;autorotate=1&amp;di=4dab83d9c34d5c5c6605e95677eb778f&amp;quality=100&amp;size=b870_10000&amp;src=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.rmb.bdstatic.com%2F635125b6c22b921a27b338e2bf28bdbf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimg01.bdimg.com%2Ftimg%3Fpacompress%26imgtype%3D1%26sec%3D1439619614%26autorotate%3D1%26di%3D4dab83d9c34d5c5c6605e95677eb778f%26quality%3D100%26size%3Db870_10000%26src%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fpic.rmb.bdstatic.com%252F635125b6c22b921a27b338e2bf28bdbf.jpeg&h=544cf691&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國家經營不善,政治政策方面要負最大責任,而負責監測政策制定政策既議會比陳蔣宋孔既人控制曬,國家部門又係陳蔣宋孔控制,銀行又係陳蔣宋孔控制,其實民國既五權分立有同冇一樣,已經變成五為一體,同以前封建一樣,話得事既人依然係果幾個人,人民始終係奴隸.<br />\n<br />\n當然,我已經預想到連登仔話因為共產黨搞搞震先會咁,先會令到國民黨經營不善,國民黨本性好優秀正義blablabla<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n根本就兩督屎,兩邊都仆街,兩邊都臭,點解連登仔會吹奏國民黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc269ca573ed622e85e45753903fbcd3e8f66ca5","tid":763664,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T10:16:12.000Z","msg":"白色恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85fea60b1a0f8111bf5326901a0ed74b3dc440af","tid":763664,"uid":36696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T10:16:46.000Z","msg":"樓主因住啲大中華膠入嚟咬你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e4d09f66c748945c649e65c6c233cdd7219ba09","tid":763664,"uid":150609,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T10:17:29.000Z","msg":"國民黨奶緊共啦-.-<br />\n<br />\n馬總桶"},{"pid":"76befd5bb75937bea18ff4e097c5babfec7580b5","tid":763664,"uid":34352,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T10:20:30.000Z","msg":"國民黨係掂又何來有共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比個細嘅食左個大"},{"pid":"d741adc3fc2a86a9681265ebe4f70a7db7c7b9ce","tid":763664,"uid":3912,"like":39,"dislike":3,"score":36,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T10:56:01.000Z","msg":"又係呢啲垃圾招數<br />\n到底幾時有連登仔吹奏過國民黨？"},{"pid":"26fe9aeb78974a01a81283668f4fbda2f1641dea","tid":763664,"uid":59283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T10:59:27.000Z","msg":"都係屎"},{"pid":"adac695f2e84762d1817d16fe78969cf5d2e1d14","tid":763664,"uid":34742,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:00:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"405294089cff80eabc071d818ab8691fef2019a2","tid":763664,"uid":15370,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"d741adc3fc2a86a9681265ebe4f70a7db7c7b9ce","tid":763664,"uid":3912,"like":39,"dislike":3,"score":36,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T10:56:01.000Z","msg":"又係呢啲垃圾招數<br />\n到底幾時有連登仔吹奏過國民黨？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:01:59.000Z","msg":"打稻草人"},{"pid":"d5e088237e90ae872571e41dbf97275ad1aa7ae3","tid":763664,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d741adc3fc2a86a9681265ebe4f70a7db7c7b9ce","tid":763664,"uid":3912,"like":39,"dislike":3,"score":36,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T10:56:01.000Z","msg":"又係呢啲垃圾招數<br />\n到底幾時有連登仔吹奏過國民黨？"},"citedBy":1,"rep